data.description: The quiet countryside in Blackberry Hills is back on the market! Buyers backed out prior to any inspections due to the school district not fitting their needs with no fault to the seller. 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms with a mother-in-law Suite! The 2 primary bedrooms have ensuite baths! Details include open living and dining room spaces with wood burning fireplace and vaulted ceiling. The kitchen has been remodeled with updated appliances, electric cooktop and oven, microwave, trash compactor and granite countertops and pantry plus planning desk. Beautiful sunroom overlooking the backyard! Great location on 1.25 acres in North Edmond! Water well and septic. Great opportunity to own a nice piece of the Oklahoma country living! SELLERS HAVE ASSUMABLE VA LOAN AT 3.5%!
